Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:08.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.00,0:00:16.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:33.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:36.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:39.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Sir, I don't know what's going on here,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.00,0:00:41.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,but I think you're way out of line.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:44.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:49.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,From the look of you,\Nyou're that State Alchemist, aren't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:51.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,You're a State Alchemist?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:55.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,So we can't let someone like you pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:00:58.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,That's what.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:01:02.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,That suits us just fine, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:11.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Yeah, now I have a legitimate reason\Nto kick some butt.
